title: How to Master the Natural Makeup Look | Macy’s
description:
This spring, it’s all about going au naturel. We’re not talking about ditching makeup all together, but instead creating a look that’s so fresh and dewy, people may just wonder if you really did wake up like this. To pull off this barely there makeup look we’re turning to makeup artist Eman to teach us her gorgeous nude face technique. Plus, she has a few tips on how to create the perfect nude matte lip, too!
